Core Capabilities
- Multi-client interface isolation allowing parallel stream rendering and connection logging loops.
- Real-time token tracking and platform authentication headers contextually managed on-the-fly.
- Broad layout compatibility across standard modern video format APIs (VP9, AV1, H.264) and audio descriptors.
- Smart layout customization templates and macro support for custom ad-container hiding adjustments.
- Highly optimized IPC (Inter-Process Communication) loops engineered to handle live comment tickers safely.

